HEADWORD: Nitrogelatin
<hw>Ni`tro*gel"a*tin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Nitro-</ets> + <ets>gelatin</ets>.]</ety> <def>An explosive
consisting of gun cotton and camphor dissolved in nitroglycerin.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>nitrogelatine</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

